&lt;p&gt;The key insight: &lt;strong&gt;series rotation&lt;/strong&gt;. Instead of randomly picking what to write about, each slot cycles through series. Monday morning Dev.to is always "Blog Ops", Tuesday is "The Lazy Developer", and so on. This keeps every series moving forward consistently.&lt;/p&gt;

